{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act18d0_level_act18d0_02_beg","storyGroup":"act18d0","storySort":3,"storyDependence":"act18d0_level_act18d0_01_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WD-2","storyName":"绿洲惊雷","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"某个无名乌萨斯村庄内，一位神秘的医生正在为急性感染者做应急手术。此时，她的过去找到了她——石棺事件遇难者家属莉莉娅，想要凯尔希帮她完成复仇。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act18d0/level_act18d0_02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act18d0_02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":1,"next":3,"characters":["？？？","乌萨斯村民","莉莉娅","病患","凯尔希"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"2上","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"Text","text":"十七年前","id":7},{"type":"Text","text":"3:09 P.M.  天气/晴","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"乌萨斯，移动城市切尔诺伯格主航道西北侧一百四十七公里，村落","id":9},{"type":"Dialog","id":10},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":11},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_snowconutry_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":12},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":13},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":14,"musicid":0},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":15},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"村庄......","id":17,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":18},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"快，快，医生说要准备温水！","id":21,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"这突然要上哪儿去找温水......问问玛莎，问问她家早上烧的水还有剩的没。","id":22,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"皇帝在上，求求您保佑老头子吧......","id":23,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"打扰一下......这里发生什么事了，您说的医生是？","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"唔，你......您是谁？","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"您从哪里来......您这身打扮，是城里来的？抱歉，抱歉，我们现在得忙着救人......您不介意的话，跟我往这儿走，至少能坐一坐。","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"没关系......我就是来找那个医生的。她叫什么？","id":30,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"您......您不会是来......","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"她只是一个可疑的医生，你们很信任她吗？","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"可她......可只有她能救好老头子啦，求求您，我求求您，至少现在，她只是个救人的医生啊。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......我不是来抓她的。我只是找她有点事。","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"能为我带路吗？","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"我......我不知道......","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我也算是个医生。也许我能帮上忙。","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"哦，看您这身打扮，驮兽也知道您的才学......","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......你可以先告诉凯尔希医生，告诉她，她的学生莉莉娅来探望她了，问问她需不需要帮手。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"啊，原来您知道医生的名字，您是叫莉莉娅，是吗？好的，好的，真是个好听的名字，您请稍等，我这就去。","id":49,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"啊，喂！别忘了让玛莎送温水来！","id":50,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":53},{"type":"character","id":54},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":55},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_snowconutryinside","screenadapt":"coverall","id":56},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"呃，呃啊......","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"咬紧牙关，坚持住。","id":60,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"character","id":61},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"呃啊啊啊——咕——","id":63,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":64},{"type":"dialog","id":65},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":66},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......凯尔希......","id":68,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#2","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......","id":70,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#3","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"这是什么情况？","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"遭到野兽袭击，应急处理罢了。","id":74,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"刀。","id":76,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"哎，呃......在、在哪里......我找不着......","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"这儿，给。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":82,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......感染生物？","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"是的。","id":86,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"2","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......会感染吗？","id":88,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"1","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"大部分感染生物都比人们想象的要干净，看齿痕，应该是附近游荡的獠兽。","id":90,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"2","id":91},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......但如果是误触了活性源石的獠兽......","id":92,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"1","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"感染生物也许有办法和各种病菌和平共处，但是人类不行。","id":94,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"情况很严重，不光是源石感染，还有坏死症状。","id":96,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"character","id":97},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"痛......好痛......","id":99,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"冷静些，深呼吸。","id":101,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"character","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"呼——喝——呼——","id":103,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"呼吸困难，可能是血栓。都是急性矿石病的症状。","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"但，但不是身上冒出石头才是矿石病吗！？老头子他这不是没事吗！？","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"某些情况下，感染源会在血液里迅速循环，不会像普通的矿石病那样出现体表源石结晶，而是在短时间内迅速加剧感染症状。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#6","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"如果不靠药物抑制......唔。","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"皇帝在上，皇帝在上......","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#6","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......","id":115,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你学得很多。","id":117,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"注射器，在那个灰色的药箱里。","id":119,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"给......你都随身带着这种抑制药物吗？","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"总有必要的时候。","id":123,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"character","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"等等......咳咳，医、医生......这个，很贵吗？","id":125,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":126},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"都什么时候啦！？","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不贵，不用在意。现在当务之急是抑制你的急性矿石病反应，避免源石结晶粉尘的爆发。","id":130,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你不希望村里的其他人因为你而受难，对吧？","id":131,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"character","id":132},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"......唔！","id":134,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"稳住呼吸，别紧张。","id":136,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你不会有事的。","id":137,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"character","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"呃，好的......","id":139,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"嘶——哈——","id":140,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"呃......嘶......医、医生......我不想......变成感染......咳咳......感染者......","id":142,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"很遗憾。","id":144,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"character","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"我......呜......我......咳咳......咳咳咳......","id":146,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#2","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"窒息，但我们没有呼吸机......","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#2","focus":"1","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这里什么都没有，但不代表我们什么都不该做。把喷雾拿来。","id":150,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"医生！医生！求求你救救这个糟老头子吧！","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"在源石粉尘渗入他创口的那一瞬间，他注定会成为一名感染者，而我能做的只是尽力延续他的生命。","id":154,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"character","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"咳咳，咳咳咳——呼，哈——","id":156,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"2","id":157},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"抑制剂还没有生效吗！？","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"1","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"考虑到患者年龄，抑制剂本身就有极大风险，保持耐心。","id":161,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"character","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"......哈......哈......","id":163,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#3","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"呼吸平稳些了......","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"病好了吗？他的病好了吗？","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_168_1#3","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"如果是指急性症状的话，也许是的。但如果是说矿石病的话，我们无能为力，谁都无能为力。","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":170},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"怎么会......那如果纠察队的老爷来了......","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"character","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"那就，那就把我......把我供出去！我本来就没几年好活了......感染就感染吧......别让那些读过书的小伙子四处乱说就行......","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":175},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"不！不会的，不会的，只要把你藏好，不会有人发现的，大家都会把你藏好的。","id":177,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"医生，谢谢您了，医生，虽然这不是最好的结果，但我们......我们也没有什么东西可以报答您......","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这只是医生的职责。成为感染者之后的道路......才是你们需要考虑的。很抱歉，环境不允许我做更多。","id":180,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......抑制剂起效了，但是伤口仍旧有感染，会导致他的血栓恶化......也许我们得手术切除......","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你的判断是正确的，老先生，咬紧牙关。","id":184,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"character","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"病患","text":"啊，好......好......呃啊，唔——！","id":186,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"50","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":187},{"type":"Dialog","id":188},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":189},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_iceforest_2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":190},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":191},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"辛苦了，莉莉娅。","id":193,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"2","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......好久不见，凯尔希所长。","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"好久不见，边走边说吧。","id":197,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"也许......你并不愿意在那场屠杀之后还这样与我对话，但我打心底里庆幸你还活着。","id":198,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......在那之后，你一直躲藏在这里？","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"那边的山丘上，可以眺望到切尔诺伯格的高楼。如果是我，不会选在一个离航道这么近的地方藏身。","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我只是暂作停留而已。","id":203,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"你......你在那之后都做了些什么？","id":205,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不希望仇恨在你们之间继续连绵流淌。特别是，这股仇恨不光会使人采取自毁般的行径，更会招来那些凶手的直接报复。","id":207,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......你是在故意说给我听的，对不对？","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不否认，莉莉娅。但是......","id":211,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":212},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":213},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":214},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"凯尔希医生，您出门？","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"啊，这位......","id":217,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"是我的学生，不必紧张，她是来接我的。","id":219,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"啊，原来是这样......不过，说是来接您的？","id":221,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"皇帝在上呀......您还是要走了吗？","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......","id":224,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"如果您要走了，请一定要告诉我们一声呀！您治好了我们的女儿，至少，请让我们为您送行！","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"会的。","id":228,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯村民","text":"啊，好，好，那我们就不打扰二位了，离开之前，请一定要告诉我，凯尔希医生......请别忘了。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialog","id":231},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":232},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":234},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_iceforest_2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":236},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"你似乎很受这里人的欢迎。","id":239,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"他们表露出了足够多的善意，我只是尽了医生的本职而已。","id":241,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......其实他们的生活才是乌萨斯大部分人的面貌。待在研究所里久了，我们都忘了不少。","id":243,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"即使刻意靠近移动城市的航道，也并不能为他们带来机遇与繁荣。","id":245,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"恰恰相反，附庸权力的乡绅土豪为纠察队剥削贫民提供了更便利的土壤。","id":246,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"所以他们连一位医学院毕业的普通医生都请不起，一场普通的流感就能杀死一位年轻的少女。","id":247,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"你的视野很广阔，是啊，一直如此......你还会治疗流感？我以为......","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你以为我是个对着论文和数据指指点点的科学家。","id":251,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"2","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"老实说，你比我想的更接近一个医生。","id":253,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"1","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"也许我从一开始就是个医生。只是医治的对象和抗争的病灶在不断变化。","id":255,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"2","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"所以你的学生才会那么信任你。","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......莉莉娅。","id":259,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你的女儿呢？","id":260,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"2","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......我把她交给了我的朋友。她和这一切都毫无瓜葛。","id":262,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"她还......那么小，她还不会说话，她甚至还不会行走......","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我就这么抛弃了我的孩子。","id":264,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"1","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你本可以不这么做，如果你希望和路易莎隐姓埋名地生活下去的话——","id":266,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"你应该知道我的想法，凯尔希所长。","id":268,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我只是想要阻止你。但如果你的女儿都做不到让你停下脚步，也许我的话你也听不进去。","id":270,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"2","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......是啊。你挺清楚的呀。","id":272,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Dialog","id":273},{"type":"character","id":274},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_snowconutry_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":276},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"今年的冬天很冷。","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"万比洛夫的父亲因为儿子的死发了疯，他在他湖边的阁楼里圈养着羽兽，每天都幻想着自己和儿子打猎的时光。","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"伊利亚的孩子，柳德米拉，她也还小，但她已经足以理解一部分无法挽回的事情，没人知道她如今到底过得如何。","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"还有罗曼诺维奇，他的家人们变卖了所有的财产，离开了那座城市。即使他的兄弟根本不相信什么事故，但有人让他们闭嘴了。","id":282,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":284,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......至于更多人，警察提供了一份事无巨细的事故报告。","id":286,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"在那份“事故伤亡名单”里，没有任何人离开切尔诺伯格的研究所。一场实验事故引发的连锁反应，还有军方提供的尸体身份鉴定报告。","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"但某种直觉告诉我......有人活着。","id":288,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"直觉？","id":290,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"因为在那之后，所有受害者家属都或多或少受到了匿名的帮助——以及警告。","id":292,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......我不觉得那个怯懦无能的鲍里斯侯爵，或是谢尔盖那个叛徒会有什么慈悲之心，所以，一定有其他知情者活了下来。","id":293,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"可直到三年后的今天我才找到你，凯尔希所长，我才找到你，你藏得可真好，你甚至能骗过秘密警察的眼睛......","id":294,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"在刑侦方面，他们过于依赖乌萨斯最新的技术，但这反而为我创造了机会。","id":296,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"2","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"当然......你是个公认的天才，无与伦比的科研领袖，否则大家也不会对你心服口服。","id":298,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"1","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——请如实告诉我，莉莉娅，有多少人参与了你的计划？","id":300,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......六七个吧。也许更多，我们不敢公然团结在一起，会被抓住把柄。","id":302,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"包括我在内。所有人都在那场“事故”中失去了一些无法挽回的东西。","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你从什么时候开始谋划这件事的？","id":305,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"从我得知第四集团军的爪牙在那个研究所射出的第一枚弩箭，就罪恶地贯穿了我孩子的父亲的脖颈时，从那时开始。","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"莉莉娅......","id":311,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我并非有勇无谋。虽然因为身体原因，我和你们共事的时间很短，但是......我也做到了一些事情，比如——","id":313,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你找到了万尼亚大公的所在，那所建立在移动城市之外的松心山谷疗养院。","id":315,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#2","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"唔......","id":317,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#2","focus":"1","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"而这位第四集团军前参谋，也极可能是石棺事件幕后推动人之一的乌萨斯大公，也许正处于他漫长的征战生涯中守备最脆弱的时期。","id":319,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你想进行一次刺杀，莉莉娅，但这次复仇依旧算得上“有勇无谋”。","id":320,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"2","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......呵。","id":322,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我算是明白，为什么丈夫他......阿斯特罗夫他会那么钦佩你了。","id":323,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#5","focus":"1","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"但你要知道，莉莉娅，杀死一位年迈的大公根本没有任何意义。","id":325,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"也许从一开始，那个年迈到在演讲时需要注射强心剂的万尼亚就不是真正的凶手。","id":326,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"2","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我知道，凯尔希，我知道......","id":328,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"2","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"可难道我把路易莎托付给他人的时候，就只是为了一个理性的结果，一次所谓的正义的审判吗？你不会猜不到的，凯尔希。","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"1","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"盲目的复仇只会使你短视。","id":332,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#6","focus":"2","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"凯尔希，凯尔希，也许你不会明白。","id":334,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"路易莎甚至都没学会说“爸爸”。","id":335,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#6"},{"type":"Dialog","id":336},{"type":"character","id":337},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":338},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_indoor_u","screenadapt":"coverall","id":339},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":340},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":341},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"坐吧。","id":342,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......你在这里呆了多久？","id":344,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不值一提的时间，莉莉娅，你的脸色很差，你需要休息。","id":346,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你是如何找到我的？","id":347,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":348},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"只是偶然......如果不是这个偶然，也许我根本发现不了你还活着。","id":349,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......柳德米拉。","id":350,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我们不愿意孩子们受到太多伤害，起先，我们是打算找柳德米拉。","id":351,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"但那时候，从柳德米拉的保姆那里得知，有人在保持着对她们的联络和帮助。是个匿名角色，但她似乎对一切都了如指掌。","id":352,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"也是这个匿名者，甚至都为她准备好了离开乌萨斯的办法。","id":353,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"那时候我就确信，还有人活着。而据我所知，能办成这件事的人，寥寥无几。","id":354,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":355},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"喝杯茶吧。","id":356,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":357},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我还以为你会迫不及待地询问我疗养院的事情。","id":358,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":359},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"莉莉娅，我想迫不及待的人，其实是你。","id":360,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":361},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"关于这件事，原来你一直都知道万尼亚身在何方......你就真的作壁上观？你应该知道他掌握着什么秘密！","id":362,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"真正的秘密已经在伊利亚的坚持下被永远封存在了那个研究所。时至今日，军队也没能从中得到半点他们垂涎的好处。","id":364,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"而万尼亚大公身患顽疾，每年冬天都会在松心山谷疗养。只要有办法混入任何一次所谓上流社会的沙龙，就不难得到这个情报。","id":365,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"......他甚至会四处夸耀那座疗养院的美丽与宽广。","id":367,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"是的。那座疗养院里有不少战功卓越的乌萨斯军人，当然，也有官僚和贵族。","id":369,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"潜入那里并暗杀一位大公，其荒唐程度并不亚于你在切尔诺伯格持刀闯入鲍里斯侯爵的宅邸，割开他的喉咙再全身而退。","id":370,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"2","id":371},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"你说的没错。但对于“官僚和贵族”们而言，那里的警戒依旧薄弱到让人蠢蠢欲动。","id":372,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1","focus":"1","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我不否认。可你怎么知道那不是一个讯号，一个万尼亚大公不再位高权重的讯号，又或者......","id":374,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":375},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"或者万尼亚大公已经被某些人安排好了命运？我说过，凯尔希，我要的不是一次公正的审判。说直白点，我渴求的是一场私刑。","id":376,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":377},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":378,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":379},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"现在不是讨论正义和道德的时候，凯尔希，只有高枕无忧的人才喜欢用“客观”做挡箭牌。","id":380,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"万尼亚大公被军方或者皇帝本人问责，变成替死鬼，或者在政斗中站错了队，遭到流放，被集团军雪藏......","id":381,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"——无论怎样，哪怕他最后惨死于绞刑架，那又与我何干呢。","id":382,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"是他推动着切尔诺伯格的一切变得更糟，我只知道，他应该付出代价，“向我们”付出代价！他是杀了我孩子父亲的凶手！","id":383,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"2","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"凯尔希！","id":385,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#4","focus":"1","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我在听......","id":387,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我已经想好了混入疗养院的方法......但我也得承认，即使那里的警戒薄弱得可疑，也不代表我们中的任何人可以轻松得手。","id":389,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我找到了一个突破口。一个在贵族疗养院当了三十几年安全负责人，却忌惮贵族而不敢轻易捞取任何油水的家伙。","id":390,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我在......同僚们的帮助下准备了一大笔钱，那个一事无成的，眼看着就要退休的老家伙一口就答应了。","id":391,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"我们花了很多力气才让他相信，我只是个乡下暴发户的女儿，为了傍上某位贵族或者将校才想进入疗养院实习工作。","id":392,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"但......","id":393,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你希望我帮你们。","id":395,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_168_1#3","focus":"2","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"是啊，无论何种形式的身份伪造都有风险，但我想，疗养院总不至于和情报机构交流密切，那么——","id":397,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"如果就连秘密警察都误以为你死了——","id":398,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莉莉娅","text":"——那死亡将使你畅通无阻。","id":399,"figure":"avg_npc_168_1#3"},{"type":"dialog","id":400},{"type":"character","id":401},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":402},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":403},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":404},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":406},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"1080年，“石棺事件”的幸存科学家，谢尔盖，成立了全新的研究所。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":407},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"同年，鲍里斯侯爵大规模扩建切尔诺伯格的工业区域。第四集团军信使史无前例地在侯爵那里吃了一记闭门羹。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":408},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"柳德米拉尚且年幼，而路易莎也只是无数普通孩子中的一员，凯尔希这么想到。她能理解莉莉娅身为一位母亲，对这些孩子复杂的、残酷的期许。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":409},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"而切尔诺伯格核心城的引擎经过了第若干次重要维护后，依旧在轰鸣转动。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":410},{"type":"subtitle","id":411},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":412},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":413},{"type":"Dialog","id":414},{"type":"Character","id":415},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":416},{"type":"Image","id":417}],"characters":["？？？","乌萨斯村民","莉莉娅","病患","凯尔希"]}